Rafa Benitez has reached his seventh European semi-final in 12 seasons with Napoli . 
  The Spaniard has won the Europa League with Chelsea and the Champions League with Valencia . 
  He guided Liverpool to the final of the competition in 2005 . 
  Napoli beat Wolfsburg 6-3 on aggregate to reach the semi-finals . 
  BeniteZ is out of contract at the end of the season and has been linked with Manchester City . 
 